Scope of This Addendum
The policy on this page explains additional disclosures required by the Personal Information Protection Act (“PIPA”) and contains information about Plarium’s service within the Republic of Korea. If you are based in the Republic of Korea, the terms set out below apply to you in addition to the terms set out in our Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.
