Opt-In and Opt-Out for Optional Personal Information Usage
Opt-In:
By engaging with our services, you may be presented with the option to opt-in to various forms of data collection and usage, such as receiving marketing communications, personalized content, and other targeted services. The specific options will be clearly explained at the point of data collection. You can provide your consent by selecting the appropriate checkbox or following the specific instructions provided in the communication or interface.
Example: When signing up for our newsletter, you will be prompted to check a box indicating your consent to receive email marketing. Alternatively, when you provide your email for marketing purposes, guidance will be provided, indicating that by clicking the "OK" or "Submit" buttons, you are giving your consent to receive marketing communications.
We will only use the data for the purposes for which you have provided your consent. If we intend to use your data for any new purpose, we will obtain your explicit consent before proceeding.
Opt-Out:
You have the right to withdraw your consent or opt-out of any specific data usage at any time. This includes opting out of receiving marketing communications, personalized content, or any other optional services that require your data.
How to Opt-Out:
Email Marketing:
You can opt-out of email marketing by clicking the "unsubscribe" link at the bottom of any marketing email you receive from us.
Account Settings:
You can manage your preferences and opt-out of specific data uses by accessing your account settings on our platform.
Contacting Us Directly:
You can contact our customer support at
https://plariumplay-support.plarium.com
or send us an email through
privacy.support@plarium.com
to request an opt-out from any data usage practice. Please specify the nature of your request to ensure we can process it effectively.
Once you opt-out, we will cease the use of your data for the specified purposes, although we may still retain and use your data as required for legitimate business needs or legal requirements.
